#: About.qml:9
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:group"
msgid "Germanisches Nationalmuseum"
msgstr "Germanisches Nationalmuseum"

#: About.qml:14
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The original Behaim globe can be visited in the <a href=\"https://www.gnm.de/"
"\">Germanisches Nationalmuseum</a> in Nuremberg, Germany."
msgstr ""
"Originálny Behaimov glóbus si môžete pozrieť v <a href=\"https://www.gnm.de/"
"\">Germanisches Nationalmuseum</a> v Norimbergu, Nemecko."

#: About.qml:20
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:group"
msgid "Map Content"
msgstr "Obsah mapy"

#: About.qml:25
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Digitized map based on orthophotographic gores by TU Vienna, 1990. "
"Germanisches Nationalmuseum and Friedrich-Alexander-Universität Erlangen-"
"Nürnberg, CC BY-SA 3.0. Ghillany map based on two planiglobes which are "
"provided as a map supplement to F.W. Ghillany's \"Geschichte des Seefahrers "
"Ritter Martin Behaim nach den ältesten vorhandenen Urkunden\", Nuremberg "
"1853. CC BY-SA 3.0."
msgstr ""
"Digitized map na základe orthophotographic gores by TU Vienna, 1990. "
"Germanisches Nationalmuseum and Friedrich-Alexander-Universität Erlangen-"
"Nürnberg, CC BY-SA 3.0. Ghillany map na základe two planiglobes which are "
"provided as a map supplement to F.W. Ghillany's \"Geschichte des Seefahrers "
"Ritter Martin Behaim nach den ältesten vorhandenen Urkunden\", Nuremberg "
"1853. CC BY-SA 3.0."

#: main.cpp:33
#, kde-format
msgid "Marble Behaim"
msgstr "Marble Behaim"

#: main.cpp:35
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Digital reproduction of a globe crafted at the time of Columbus' first sea "
"travel to the west."
msgstr ""
"Digitálna reprodukcia glóbusu vytvoreného v čase prvej námornej plavby "
"Kolumba na západ."

#: main.cpp:37
#, kde-format
msgid "© KDE Community"
msgstr "© KDE komunita"

#: main.cpp:38
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Martin Behaim's Erdapfel</p><p>The oldest existent globe of the Earth. "
"Martin Behaim and collaborators created the globe around 1492 at the time of "
"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voyages_of_Christopher_Columbus"
"\">Columbus'</a> first sea travel to the west.Hence the American continent "
"is missing on this globe.Also note the detailed inscriptions in early modern "
"German.</p><p>Please see <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erdapfel"
"\">Wikipedia: Erdapfel</a> for further information about the Behaim globe."
msgstr ""
"<p>Erdapfel Martina Behaima</p><p>Najstarší zachovaný glóbus Zeme. Martin "
"Behaim a jeho spolupracovníci vytvorili glóbus okolo roku 1492 v čase prvej "
"námornej plavby <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Voyages_of_Christopher_Columbus\">Kolumba</a> na západ. Preto na tomto "
"glóbuse chýba americký kontinent. Všimnite si tiež podrobné nápisy v ranej "
"novovekej nemčine.</p><p>Ďalšie informácie o Behaimovom glóbuse nájdete na "
"stránke <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erdapfel\">Wikipedia: "
"Erdapfel</a>."

